<p>With these upgrades, developers can now benefit from:</p>



<ul>
<li><strong>Streamlined Integration</strong>: Seamless integration with existing development environments for a smoother transition.</li>



<li><strong>Enhanced Testing Frameworks</strong>: Robust testing frameworks that enable comprehensive testing of smart contracts and decentralized applications.</li>



