<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Throughput and Scalability Improvements</h3>



<p>As ecosystem integration continues to evolve within the Polygon network, the impact on network performance becomes increasingly significant, particularly in relation to throughput and scalability improvements. </p>



<p>These improvements are crucial for meeting the demands of a growing user base and expanding ecosystem.</p>



<p>Here&#8217;s how ecosystem integration is enhancing Polygon&#8217;s network performance:</p>



