<p>These enhancements can lead to smoother transactions, lower fees, and faster confirmation times, ultimately benefiting both developers and users.</p>



<p>Additionally, the upgraded consensus mechanisms are likely to spur increased developer activity and contribute to the overall growth of the Polygon ecosystem.</p>



