<li><strong>Security Vulnerability Assessment</strong>: Simulation tools help in identifying and addressing potential security vulnerabilities within smart contracts before deployment.</li>



<li><strong>Gas Fee Optimization</strong>: Developers can use simulation tools to optimize the gas fees associated with smart contract execution on the Polygon network.</li>



